JavaScript Ping-Pong Style Vidoe Arcade Game
===

Plank?
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ getPosition(): Point
+ moveLeft()
+ moveRight()
+ getBoundingRectangle(): Rectangle
+ update()

Ball
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ setVelocity(x: number, y: number)
+ getPosition(): Point
+ update()

Obstacle
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ getBoundingRectangle(): Rectangle

Line (between two players)
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ getBoundingRectangle(): Rectangle

Player
-----------
States:
- name: string
Behaviors:
+ getName(): string
+ setName(): string

Desk
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ getBoundingRectangle(): Rectangle

ScoreBoard
-----------
States:
- scores: Array of number
- round: number
Behaviors:
+ getScore(): number
+ setScore(): number
+ getRoundNumber(): number
+ setRoundNumber(): number

Collider?
- onCollision

Point
-----------
States:
+ x
+ y

Size
-----------
States:
+ width
+ height

Rectangle
-----------
States:
- position: Point
- size: Size
Behaviors:
+ setPosition(position: Point)
+ setSize(size: Size)

Main function: Game loop